"---------------------------------------------------------------------
" FILE: .vimrc (Tiny edition)
" AUTHOR: Elliott Indiran <eindiran@uchicago.edu>
" DESCRIPTION: Config file for Vim, but without any fanciness
" CREATED: Sat 08 Jul 2017
" LAST MODIFIED: Sat 08 Jul 2017
" VERSION: 1.0.0
"---------------------------------------------------------------------
set number
set tabstop=4
set softtabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set expandtab
set autoindent
set copyindent
set ignorecase
set smartcase
set nocompatible
set hlsearch
" Show tabs not as whitespace
set list
set listchars=tab:▸·
